            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">Pakistan's Leading Talent Network</h2>
                <p class="lead">Since 2011, Cinexcs has been pushing industry boundaries and discovering exceptional talent from every corner of Pakistan.</p>
                <p>We invest in extraordinary people and their careers, providing them with opportunities to work with leading brands, designers, and media houses across the country.</p>
